_sText: Prefab by XxLeXuSxX (me) I took a hard time to get it as much perfect as possible, just for you people. Do what ever you wish with it. :) NOTE: The Glass is not breakable. Step 1: I made the .vmf into a .rar file. So, just place the .rar file in the folder 'sourcesdk_content' (F:\Valve\Steam\SteamApps\UserName\sourcesdk_content) step 2: Just extract the file and it will go automaticly to the 'mapsrc' folder (F:\Valve\Steam\SteamApps\UserName\sourcesdk_content\cstrike\mapsrc) Enjoy :)
